Deng '''kamaru''' (''mole cricket'' king Ingles) a bibilug king [[:en:Family (biology)|familia]] '''Gryllotalpidae''', insectu la o ayup-ayupan a maki kabang 3-5 cm (1-2 pulgada). Mangaragul la ampong pakabural deng karelang mata, at maki bitis la king arap a balamu pala, a bage king pamangulkul ampong pamangawe. Agiu da muring sulagpo, at makasulagpo lang anggang {{convert|8|km|mi|1}} deti neng panaun ning pamagpalipi. Makalual la king keraklan king banua, at matudtud (''hibernation'') la neng karimlan (''winter'') kareng marimlang lugal.   
Mas makuyad la pakpak deng anak a kamaru, at aliwa-liwa ing karelang itsura dependi king species o uri. Ating lupang [[durun]], at atin namang kawangis maragul a [[panas]] o matuling a "[[ane]]" neng makuyad la pakpak.

Miayaliwa la kakanan deng kamaru, alimbawa deng ulad, bulati, yamut, ampong dikut. Kayabe no man kareng mamangan kamaru deng [[ayup]], [[dagis]], [[skunk]], [[armadillo]], [[raccoon]] ampong [[:en:fox|fox]]. 
[[Image:MoleCricketLyd.png|thumb|250px|left|Ing durut ning bie o ''life cycle'' ning metung a kamaru]]
Dakal la at malapad la reng lugal nung nu ating kamaru, oneng uling neng bengi la lulual deti at alus mabilug dang bie atilu lalam gabun kareng kulkul, malagad la mung mayayakit. Mabibie la kareng asikan, dikut a mula (''lawns''), ampong pipamialungan golf (''golf courses''). Ati lu king balang continenti liban king [[Antarctica]], at maralas, tuturing dong pesti. Nanupata, king [[Aslagang Asia]], gagawan da lang pamangan. King [[Filipinas]], pikabaluan la reng [[Kapampangan (lahi)|Kapampangan]] king pamamangan kamaru.

Kareng aliwang lugal, diritak la reng kamaru uling king pangatibag ning gabun ampo ning pangasira ning karelang tutuknangan.

